.SH EXAMPLES
.IP \[bu] 2
Clear the file system cache of all nodes of current cluster.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> db.invalidateFsCache()
\f[]
.fi
.IP \[bu] 2
Clear the file system cache that out of 72 hours of \[aq]group1\[aq] nodes.
.IP
.nf
\f[C]
> db.invalidateFsCache( { GroupName: \[aq]group1\[aq] }, "72" )
\f[]
.fi
